From Boyfriends To Sibling Drama -- Everything You Missed During The KUWTK Season 13 Premiere! 
Well, guys -- the 13th season of KUWTK has officially begun! 
Although Sunday night's premiere didn't get to any of the Paris robbery stuff , there were definitely a few highlights worth mentioning. 
Khloé Kardashian and Kim Kardashian West teamed up against biggest sis Kourtney Kardashian regarding getting rid of DASH clothing store locations. Apparently there's an offer on the table to sell the chain to a department store. 
KoKo and Kimmie are ready to move on, while the 37-year-old argues the company was started right after the death of their father: 
"After dad passed away, we got Dash. Having Dash kept us together as sisters." 
Adding later: 
"It's more to us than just our store, it's something we've all built as sisters. So we can figure out the deal later, but I think for now we should get rid of New York… It's a better business decision… We want to keep Miami open." 
Eventually, Kim agreed: 
"We put so much blood, sweat and tears into this. At the end of the day it makes sense to close New York because it's so expensive… but keep Miami."
